{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"body":"Plan-review advisory triage (all 8 valid, resolved in impl/test design): (1)+(2) verify-over-exact-bytes: dsse.py exposes pae(payload_type,body)->bytes + envelope encode/decode; byte-identity test asserts decoded payload == original bytes and pae() runs over those exact bytes, not json.dumps(json.loads(...)). (3) DSSE v1.0.0 §3: envelope payload & sig are base64url-encoded; decode base64url-decodes before PAE — impl + test. (4) file_impact now set. (5)+(6) envelope encode/decode round-trip + fixed-vector decode tests added. (7) error-case edge tests: empty payload_type, malformed/missing-field envelope JSON. (8) create src/rebar/attest/__init__.py for the namespace. Re-running review-plan to re-sign after file_impact change."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783784062096217001,"uuid":"871e6c66-bfb7-4de3-8425-ceb59a49e524"}